Title: The Chair Model
Plot: Michael gets fascinated by a chair model in a catalog, leading to a desire to move on from Jan. Kevin and Andy team up to gain parking spaces back for Dunder Mifflin lost during another complex tenant's construction work.
GuestStars: Barry Sigismondi, Brooke Dillman, Paul Faust, Terrence Beasor, Sean Bury, Robert R. Shafer
